[b][center][size=6][color=#00ff00][u]Ilinalta Castle
[/u][/color][/size][/center][color=#ffff00][size=2][u]Description:[/u][/size][/color]
[/b]
Hi :)
My name is Steve.I'm just a normal guy from Slovakia, who enjoys modding...
This is my first mod for Skyrim.

This mod adds a player home to Lake Ilinalta, but currently there is no quest.

[u][b][color=#9fc5e8]HOW TO GET THERE + KEY LOCATION:[/color][/b][/u]
You'll get there by a boat near the Half moon mill.
Key to the castle door is in the tower with eagle's nest.
CASTLE CONTAINS:
[list]
[*]Bedroom
[*]Bathroom
[*]Toilet
[*]Kitchen
[*]Tomb
[*]Children room
[*]Rooftop terrace
[*]Followers room
[*]Trophy room with six mannequins
[*]Storage room
[*]Blacksmith
[*]Wizard tower
[/list]
This mod [color=#00ffff]requires[/color] [b][color=#00ffff]Skyrim[/color][/b] and [b][color=#00ffff]all DLCs[/color][/b].
I hope you enjoy it. :)
author: pitox38
